trans-unit.source: Defines the configuration file mapping for the machine configuration file.
The ConfigurationFileMap class is used to specify the path of the machine configuration file, commonly named Machine.config.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ConfigurationFileMap används för att ange sökvägen till konfigurationsfilen datorn ofta heter Machine.config.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationFileMap"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationFileMap"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationFileMap"></xref> class based on the supplied parameter.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationFileMap"> </xref> klassen baserat på den angivna parametern.

trans-unit.source: The name of the machine configuration file.
Creates a copy of the existing <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationFileMap"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Skapar en kopia av den befintliga <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationFileMap"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name of the machine configuration file name.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger namnet på namnet på datorn konfigurationsfilen.

trans-unit.source: The machine configuration file name is commonly set as Machine.config.
trans-unit.target: Namnet på datorn konfigurationsfilen anges vanligtvis som Machine.config.
